divs: Sighting DetailsMe and two friends where walking home tonight and sighted ufos. we were walking north back to our estate when we saw two strange lights in the sky. the three of us got up on a wall and where looking at them when one of them started moving left accross the sky. when it was a good bit away from the other light another one appeared next to the stationary one out of nowhere. At this point we were all freaked out and started running to a nearby park where theres a hill with a clear view of the whole city one of my friends went back home at this point. we were standing on the hill for a good while and i actually got a video of one of the lights although it was takin on my phone (very low quality video)
